ebrated Crimes\n|\nNever waste time for someone who doesn’t bother to spend time with you, but with someone who will say, time is wasted if I’m not with you.\n\n- M.\n|\nI have a really beautiful life right now, so there is no reason to be hostile. I'm a husband, a father and a man who tries to do the right thing in life and in my work.\n\n- Ice\n|\nIf you didn't understand the need for friendship or love, could you be lonely?\n\n- Laurell K. Hamilton, Cerulean Sins\n|\nFor success, optimism is more important than opportunity.\n\n- Debasish\n|\nYou fulfill your hearts universal desire for love not by accumulating, but by giving.\n\n- Debasish\n|\nWe both loved her. And you couldn't control who you loved, even if you wanted to.\n\n- Kami Garcia, Beautiful Redemption\n|\nif you cannot ponder to wonder, you will always wonder to ponder\n\n- Ernest Agyemang Yeboah, Distinctive Footprints of Life: Where Are You Heading Towards?\n|\nI can critique the bad; I can take the good, and I can add whatever I want.\n\n- Justine\n|\nAccept who you are. Don’t leave me, Willow. We are all broken, that’s how the light shines through. - Rhydian\n\n- Mira Monroe, Magick\n|\nNow is much better then was, and if and when aren't as great as now - yet.\n\n- Rodney\n|\nTrue repentence is to depart from evil. A return to God, seeking his grace for power to obey him.\n\n- Lailah\n|\nIf you believe in God, believe in Death Row East.\n\n- Tupac\n|\nWhat's a bigger mystery box than a movie theater? You go to the theater, you're just so excited to see anything - the moment the lights go down is often the best part.\n\n- J.\n|\nThe secret to unseating great power, is not to move the other direction, but to compete directly against their goals.\n\n- Bryant McGill, Simple Reminders: Inspiration for Living Your Best Life\n|\nPrayer changes things, but it ultimately changes the one who prays.\n\n- Suzanne Eller, Come with Me: Discovering the Beauty of Following Where He Leads\n|\nHave been most timid o